Package com.flipfit.bean

Class FlipFitPayment

java.lang.Object
com.flipfit.bean.FlipFitPayment
public class FlipFitPayment extends Object
Represents a payment in the FlipFit system. Each payment is associated with a booking and contains details such as payment ID and amount paid.
Author:
Arvind Yadav
